# Data

## LendingClub Loan Dataset

This project uses the LendingClub loan dataset available publicly on Kaggle.

### Download Instructions

1. Go to: [https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/wordsforthewise/lending-club](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/wordsforthewise/lending-club)
2. Download the dataset (requires a free Kaggle account)
3. Extract `loan.csv` and place it in this `data/` directory

### Expected File

```
data/
└── loan.csv        # ~1.8 GB, ~2.26M rows × 145 columns
```

The file is excluded from this repository via `.gitignore` due to its size.

### Dataset Notes

- Source: LendingClub peer-to-peer lending platform (2007–2018)
- Observations used: Loans with resolved status only (`Fully Paid`, `Charged Off`, `Default`)
- Time split used in this project:
  - **Train**: Loans issued before January 2014
  - **Test**: Loans issued January 2014 – December 2014
  - **OOT**: Loans issued January 2015 onward
